name: NFTs are dumb
description: This was something I did back when I wasn't in the NFT community. I was sitting with my friends on discord, discussing about how dumb NFTs are and how anything could be sold in the name of NFT. I just scribbled this. It's been months since I joined NFTs and one thing I realized was that it's not about the art or the money, it's about the relations and the community you form with your art. I love this place and all the people in it💗
